      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FAST FELIX (8) was a course and distance placegetter (19.79) last time also from the same draw, finishing a 1.5 lengths second in a Grade 5. Looks the one to beat on best. POP'S GIRL (4) stuck on well last time to finish 2 lengths back in third (19.88) at this track in a Grade 2/3 over 340m. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Will give a great sight again. DON'T SLIP MICK (2) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (16.18) at Launceston. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Expected to be in this for a long way. USE SOMEBODY (1) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can make amends.",
